cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.NE 

This paper deals with online convex optimization, a topic that is commonly studied in machine learning and optimization, hence the likely categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves the use of approximation algorithms and data structures, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
